sg":"即係以後有'國家證書'就賣乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4107d9ab162d0176a3aa775ae8f73b4a377bdb9f","tid":322690,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5ed737979cbe16c4fa39f5c140b07fa46ce3969","tid":322690,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸人都係咁食<br />\n<br />\n你條命重要d？<br />\n<br />\n咁講乜撚人權呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那人有冇關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那人乜柒自由民主法治都冇添，<br />\n<br />\n所以香港應該都冇？"},{"pid":"752c56f43ed187b5e67d98765b1fdf56b045eddf","tid":322690,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:02:48.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"ccf688658ac1421884b6dfda0f0a0451ae10307d","tid":322690,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"共享中國人美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e35f5583279782a30547ea2e1e6c866b2be5b93","tid":322690,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"我最期的畫面"},{"pid":"e52debcbf182de6af4e65660d94164c3f053b871","tid":322690,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最期待的畫面</blockquote>"}]}